    "John Trapp": "Only unto the land. ] This kindness these Ammonites, in after ages, very evil requited, { #Am 1:13 Jer 49:1 } dealing by them as that monster Michael Balbus dealt by the Emperor Leo Armenius, whom he slew the same night that this prince had pardoned and released him. [v_Deu_3_11]\n37. Only unto the land.] This kindness these Ammonites, in [v_Amo_1_13] after ages, very evil requited, {#Am 1:13 Jer 49:1} dealing by them as that monster Michael Balbus dealt by the Emperor Leo Armenius, whom he slew the same night that this prince had pardoned and released him."
